1C<ue5>4C<ue5>POPCORN<ql>
<styl>by <m2>By <m0>CURTIS MORGAN<ql>
<m1><styl>crline <m0>Herald Staff Writer<ql>
<m1><ep>
<m0>   <m2><ql>
